{"tid":1823592,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國宣布將中國剔出貨幣操縱國名單","createTime":"2020-01-13T23:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T23:13:31.000Z","uid":137220,"like":18,"dislike":538,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"f21f11aebae5d54569d8318a56b620354daa812d","tid":1823592,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T23:31:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2353398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2353398&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=93762357\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2353398</a><br />\n<br />\n美國與中國本周三預計簽署第一階段貿易協議前，特朗普政府將中國從貨幣操縱國名單之中移除。<br />\n<br />\n美國財政部周一發表半年度滙率報告，財長努欽(Steven Mnuchin)在聲明中表示，中國在中美第一階段貿易協議中作出可執行的承諾，願意壓抑競爭性貨幣貶值，同時採取透明及負責任的措施，避免貨幣持續疲弱。<br />\n<br />\n美方認為，隨著時間發展，中國經濟基本面好轉以及結構性改革，將支持人民幣升值。美國財政部將中國改為列入貨幣觀察名單。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通想降溫？"},{"pid":"62b4a9e093506d15ed9e3be402b57382707e930c","tid":1823592,"uid":321977,"like":61,"dislike":27,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T23:33:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾老美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ddd8d8445b598a22ed4962a1355e9ad01b8fb3","tid":1823592,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T23:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b893868a3862748784865542a1d3c5a97d992f50","tid":1823592,"uid":137220,"like":57,"dislike":5,"score":52,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T23:37:11.000Z","msg":"係咪代表唔會玩貨幣戰<br />\n<br />\n之前講到新冷戰咁，依家因為中東問題就讓步？？"},{"pid":"601f0a0930f065d492af6fa3b6467b106b1d07ca","tid":1823592,"uid":264992,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T23:39:22.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦都列咗操縱國乜都無做過，都係手段黎"},{"pid":"c690bfbc938a040e5fb22fad1d190318e76744a9","tid":1823592,"uid":29918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2